Leannie
Hanoi, Vietnam1,421 contributions
Best day trip we done in Da Nang
The trip here was not planned at all in advance but turned out to be one of the best things we did. We caught a grab from our hotel and they drove us to the parking area, the roads are rather windy but had fab views as you went up. When we arrived we saw a few monkeys wandering around which was great. Really surprised that there is no entrance fee for here. What we loved was how much there was too see, the stunning views and how quiet it was as it was so large and spread out. Happily spent about an hour here, probably could have done longer if it wasn't the middle of of day and really hot
