Serenity Now!
Jan 2023 ‚Ä¢ Solo
I‚Äôm in awe! The largest Lady Buddha I‚Äôve ever seen. Lady Buddha is the protector of Danang, as she has the power to re-route potential dangerous typhoon in a different direction. She is highly revered for the love she has for the people of Danang. The beautiful bonsai plants adored her lady. When visiting, make sure you truly take a good look at how intricate these plants are. I so enjoyed it so much. As I do my mindfulness, I had the chance to touch these amazing plants. The beautiful blue sky complimented the Lady. I can see Lady Buddha from my hotel room. I thank her for caring for Danang.
Remember, take lots of pictures here to take home to remind you of a serene place.
