Well worth a visit
Jan 2023 ‚Ä¢ Couples
Use Grab app to get picked up in Danang, and consider a round trip as it can get busy at the parking lot. We didn‚Äôt do round trip though and were still fine in booking another Grab once we‚Äôd done.
Spent in total about 60-90 mins here walking around the statue, pagoda and admiring the views. Can also watch the monkeys but be careful as we saw one or two getting angry at stupid tourists trying to get too close.
No entry fee and expect many tourists here, but all in all absolutely worth a trip.
