Dreamon21
Hong Kong, China62 contributions
Good Side Trip
Feb 2024 ‚Ä¢ Family
The pagoda in Son Tra is not very far from Da Nang but there are some hilly roads to climb if you drive or ride a bike. So to make things easier and relaxing we just booked a day tour with other side trips. Our guide gave us sufficient time to visit and take pictures. It is indeed a good place to take beautiful pictures if you like taking pictures otherwise you do not need to stay long in that place. It was winter when we went there so it was very windy and chilly with a bit of rain, so you need to check the weather before going there at different times or season. There are many figurine character statues and the bonsais are very well kempt and beautiful.
