Apart from Lady Buddha and temples nothing special
Feb 2020 ‚Ä¢ Couples
Nice little trip, lots of sculptures and temples.
- no entry!!
Guarded parking available, no pay only donation, you pay what you want.
Steep way up, take scooter with minimum 90cc.
Drinks are possible to buy there.
There is a man walking around the assembly who wants money for donation purposes and will first ask you to fill a survey about the location and your satisfaction.
Not sure if he is legit or a scam.
